title: Michigan St. hero Watts-Jackson was in 'pure pain' when he scored
text: Michigan St. hero Watts-Jackson was in 'pure pain' when he scored Thursday, 22 October 2015 (5 minutes ago) Jalen Watts-Jackson says he felt "pure pain" after reaching the end zone last weekend when he injured his hip while scoring the winning touchdown for Michigan State on a desperate fumble return against Michigan.
